The paper deals with the design of a communication system for aeronautical applications, which involves the use of large-scale antenna arrays and link adaptation. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), or Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves the use of analytical expressions and simulation results to evaluate the performance of the proposed system, which suggests that it could also belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) or Architecture (cs.AR) sub-categories.
